    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a reliable choice for a daily driver, though it does show signs of its age and use. The exterior has several visible scratches and a minor dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows some wear on the upholstery and a few stains on the carpet. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it may require some routine maintenance soon to keep it in peak shape. All major systems like the air conditioning and radio are functional, making this a solid, budget-friendly option for someone looking for dependable transportation.",
