    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic deal. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This chassis has been meticulously maintained with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery through the rear wheels. It sits on a refreshed suspension setup with polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in response and reduced deflection. Recent service includes rod bearing replacement and a valve adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain remains within tight tolerances. This is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s analog peak, ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Reliable engine. Clean interior. Recent service history included. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. Meticulously cared for and primarily garage-kept, the exterior retains a deep luster with only the slightest evidence of careful road use. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin featuring premium upholstery that remains supple, showing only minimal wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster typical for its age. Mechanically, it performs flawlessly; the engine pulls strong, and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. All maintenance is strictly up to date, including a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. With plenty of tread on the tires and responsive, firm brakes, this car is ready for its next owner to drive away with complete confidence. It represents a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking a high-quality driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
